long_description: Sporting classic styling, the women's Fjallraven Keb Fleece Vest warms your core with a stretchy polyester/wool blend that'll see you through many an outdoor adventure. Fleece is made of polyester for lightweight durability and wool for natural breathability and temperature regulation; elastane adds stretch. Low-bulk flatlock seams and chin guard offer comfort. Fjallraven Keb Fleece Vest for women has real-leather trim.
